                     <interp inst="t17831210-120-off611" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously making an assault on the King's highway, upon 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-120-victim1221" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Anderson
                        <interp inst="t17831210-120-victim1221" type="surname" value="Anderson"></interp>
